text: Selena Gomez `loved` being linked to Cara Delevingne Friday, 16 October 2015 (8 minutes ago) *Washington D.C., Oct. 16(ANI): Selena Gomez has recently opened up on the speculations about her romance with Cara Delevingne and it looks like that she loved the rumours.* Washington D.C., Oct. 16(ANI): Selena Gomez has recently opened up on the speculations about her romance with Cara Delevingne and it looks like that she loved the rumours. The 23-year-old songstress said in an interview that she didn't mind that as for that moment people were not talking about other people in her life, reports People magazine. Talking about Delevingne, the 'Good For You' hit-maker said that she is incredible as she is fun and extremely adventurous, just the way she wants herself to be sometimes.
